Product Catalog Management

Use Dynamic Options to Add All Products Based On a Product... 
Maximize Product Reach with Translated Product and Product Category...
Accurately Represent Monetary Values and Percentages in Product...
Alter Product Attribute Values Through Slider Controls
Personalize Product Catalog Management Objects with Custom Fields
Other Changes in Product Catalog Management

Product Discovery

Set up product discovery faster by using the new predefined pricing and qualification procedure templates. 
Quickly Create Pricing Procedures and Qualification Procedures
Clone the new predefined Product Discovery Pricing Procedure and Product Discovery Qualification Procedure templates from the Expression Set Templates page, and then customize them according to your business requirements.

Supercharge Product Browsing Experience for Your Partners and Customers
You can now add the Product List, Product Details, Product Attribute Details, and Product Bundle Details components to Experience Cloud site pages. 
Fine-Tune Product Browsing Experience
Provide only the required options and information to your sales reps when they browse products.
Use Pricing and Qualification Procedures Only When Relevant
Enable or disable the usage of pricing and qualification procedures for Product Discovery.

Easily Add Products to Quotes and Orders
Sales reps can directly select products from catalog pages, and then create quotes or orders with the selected products. 
Browse and Add Products with Derived Pricing
Sales reps can now browse and add products that are priced based on another pricing source, such as a product or an asset.
Select and Add Products Faster
With a single click, sales reps, partners, and customers can select all the qualified products from the displayed list of products by using the All Products checkbox.
title: Product Discovery Enhancements
